singapor welcom new lme aluminium contract move singapor welcom the london metal exchang 's ( lme ) deci to list singapor as a deliveri point for the lme 's new dollar-denomin aluminium contract . tay thiam peng , manag for intern trade at the trade develop board , said the deci would boost singapor 's imag as a major deliveri port . `` we hope thi will encourag more metal trader to set up shop here and that singapor can becom a deliveri port for other metal as well , `` he said . the new contract , to start trade on june 1 , is lme ' first dollar-contract .